			>
			<DIV>Cleric self buff has the same mana regen as 9, but doesnt stack with focus.&nbsp; So without focus around self + virt yields substantially better hps with the same mana regen.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>And I guess I should also add that lower level clerics may value the extra bit of mana regen that 9 gives over the lower level self buffs.&nbsp; I was comparing in the 61-65 range because that's where you'll find all the buffs we've been discussing.&nbsp; 47+ could get blessing of 9 and gain substantial mana regen.&nbsp; 55-60 (wherever the next self buff down is would yield 2 mana regen vs a few hundred hps, and at the top there's literally no point in 9 without a shaman nearby.</DIV>
								<p><div style="width: 100%; height: 120; overflow: hidden;">
								
							Laurri<br>(70 Cleric - Circle of Eternity - Veeshan)
