<DIV><STRONG><FONT color=#cc0000></FONT></STRONG>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>This is really a burden for the lower level clerics.&nbsp; By level 65 it's just an additional money sink and use of inventory slots, for clerics that already have to carry lots of non-stackable invis potions, levi potions, shrink device, and invis device, because we have no utility spells either!&nbsp; <img src='/i/smilies/16x16_smiley-sad.gif' width=16 height=16 border=0></DIV>
