		" 
			>
			<DIV></DIV>
<DIV>Take a couple minutes to read thru the other class concerns and issues. If our biggest problem right now is having to carry around a couple stacks of peridots, I think we're doing pretty darn good. </DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>If your complaint that this is a "burden" on clerics, think about what the other classes have to lug around too. Here's a few I have experience with:</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>My Cleric <BR>&nbsp;- 60x Peridots <BR>&nbsp;- 20x Mana Batteries (GVD) <BR>&nbsp;- 2x InvisPotions (for emergencies)<BR>&nbsp;- 20x Misty Thicket Picnics<BR>&nbsp;- 20x Qeynos Tea</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>My Wizard <BR>&nbsp;- 40x Peridots (SpellShield)<BR>&nbsp;- 40x Opals (Disinigrate)<BR>&nbsp;- 20x Misty Thicket Picnics<BR>&nbsp;- 20x Qeynos Tea</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>My Necro <BR>&nbsp;- 60x Peridots<BR>&nbsp;- 60x BoneChips <BR>&nbsp;- 40x Coffins<BR>&nbsp;- 20x Essence Emeralds<BR>&nbsp;- 20x Fish Scales<BR>&nbsp;- 20x Misty Thicket Picnics<BR>&nbsp;- 20x Qeynos Tea</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>My Warrior<BR>&nbsp;- 20x Mana Batteries (GVD)<BR>&nbsp;- 2x InvisPotions (for emergencies)<BR>&nbsp;- 1x IVU Potion (10dose)<BR>&nbsp;- 1x Gate Potion (10dose)<BR>&nbsp;- 2x Shrink Potions (10dose)<BR>&nbsp;- 60x Arrows<BR>&nbsp;- 80x Arrow Parts<BR>&nbsp;- 20x Halas Pies<BR>&nbsp;- 20x Grobb Liquidized Meat</DIV>
<DIV><BR>Honestly, it's not that big of a deal, it's just part of the game for alot more than just clerics. I'll agree clerics tend to spend some of them faster, but honestly, it's only 10pp a shot. At level 52 that can put a troublesome dent in your budget, but for the folks concerned with the 66-70 OoW spells? Please.. </DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>And don't forget that with HoV and MGB, they've already thrown us a bone. Where&nbsp;ya once might have had to spend 1 peridot for every single person in a raid, you can do everyone at once for 2 of them.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>	
